column5: just picked up a brand new calcutta te 100 dc off of craigslist. it's really sweet.  i thought i'd share the link with you if you are interested. it's a great price. the dude's got a few left. i can't imagine getting it for a better price.  http://toronto.en.craigslist.ca/tor/spo/1632491660.html
they are a great reel and that's a great price too
I agree, great reel and great price but the line capacity is to small for my liking.  Dirk
yeah me too if I ever see a deal like that for the 250 dc, I will be all over it I already have the  SHIMANO CALAIS  200 DC
The bloody handles on the wrong side!!!
I have the 200, amazing reel even at double the price I paid.
